query:
SELECT
            identity_id AS "identity_id: IdentityId",
            unit_id AS "unit_id: UnitId",
            data AS "data: Json<MixerPreferences>",
            created_at AS "created_at: DateTime<Utc>",
            updated_at AS "updated_at: DateTime<Utc>"
        FROM
            mixer_config
        WHERE
            identity_id = ?1 AND
            unit_id = ?2
